{"tid":1254064,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［別人笑我太瘋癲］阿根廷走靚線，下場對8強最弱隊伍委內瑞拉，這次入硬四強了","createTime":"2019-06-24T02:17:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T09:47:12.000Z","uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"f658d12aee543ca1ed6fbe70be97473c2657b06b","tid":1254064,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:17:55.000Z","msg":"當全世界人都認為阿根廷出線無望，美洲盃奪冠無望嘅時候。球王美斯所帶領阿根廷再次展現一絲曙光。經過尋晚嘅比賽阿根廷以小組第二名出線。<br />\n<br />\n進入八強將於6月29日，對上a組嘅委內瑞拉。<br />\n<br />\n今次對阿根廷黎講可謂因禍得福。對陣8強魚腩隊委內瑞拉,<br />\n美斯見到呢一隊簡直係笑逐顏開， <br />\n我諗除左可以出線之外，呢一份都係美斯生日最大嘅禮物啦。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R8DrU1P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR8DrU1P.jpg&h=68db884c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d90e7b79641c775e5b3832d5b10b0f85cb963f4e","tid":1254064,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:21:21.000Z","msg":"球王美斯走線又要你地班名宿教？<br />\n乜撚嘢退出國家隊？<br />\n連登仔真係唔識波，依家走到條最靚嘅線。<br />\n美斯下場可以留力，用最輕鬆嘅比賽進入四強。<br />\n依家剩兩場就拿美洲杯了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e84ff6e83bb0ec6b3f5193afbf6f7eea4d0a3b","tid":1254064,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:22:13.000Z","msg":"嬴到巴西就無得輸"},{"pid":"fddf568be21e1da80a48671a5918e7963bc0d8ad","tid":1254064,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"70e84ff6e83bb0ec6b3f5193afbf6f7eea4d0a3b","tid":1254064,"uid":124439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:22:13.000Z","msg":"嬴到巴西就無得輸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T02:24:13.000Z","msg":"巴西冇咗尼馬， 踢委內瑞拉都係打和。<br />\n阿根廷食硬你委內瑞拉， <br />\n巴西你 委內瑞拉都贏唔到 ，贏唔贏到阿根廷呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"